9937665/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2269937665/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2269937665/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2269937665","tinyui":"/x/AYBMhw","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2269937665","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2269937665/GitHub+Guidelines","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2269937665"}}],"macroRenderedOutput":{},"body":{"storage":{"value":"<p>The purpose of this document is to provide guidance on configuring Github reminders, which is essential to ensure the smooth functioning of the development process. Code review plays a critical role in ensuring the quality and accuracy of the code, and timely completion of code reviews is crucial to meet project deadlines.</p><h2>Steps</h2><ol start=\"1\"><li><p>Go to the Github reminders section using this <a href=\"https://github.com/settings/reminders\">LINK</a>.</p></li><li><p>Navigate to the reminders configuration section for the desired organization.<br /></p><ac:image ac:align=\"center\" ac:layout=\"center\" ac:original-height=\"277\" ac:original-width=\"802\" ac:width=\"646\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"Screenshot 2023-04-21 at 14.38.51-20230421-173916.png\" ri:version-at-save=\"1\" /></ac:image><p /></li><li><p>Authorize Slack Workspace<br /></p><ac:image ac:align=\"center\" ac:layout=\"center\" ac:original-height=\"602\" ac:original-width=\"801\" ac:width=\"408\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"image (3)-20230421-192321.png\" ri:version-at-save=\"1\" /></ac:image><p /><ac:image ac:align=\"center\" ac:layout=\"center\" ac:original-height=\"404\" ac:original-width=\"454\" ac:width=\"306\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"image (4)-20230421-192844.png\" ri:version-at-save=\"1\" /></ac:image><p /><ac:image ac:align=\"center\" ac:layout=\"center\" ac:original-height=\"619\" ac:original-width=\"632\" ac:width=\"374\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"image (5)-20230421-193115.png\" ri:version-at-save=\"1\" /></ac:image></li><li><p>Select the Moove It workspace and configure the daily and real-time reminders according to individual preferences. Afterward, click on the button to create the reminder.<br /></p><ac:image ac:align=\"center\" ac:layout=\"center\" ac:original-height=\"865\" ac:original-width=\"802\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"Screenshot 2023-04-21 at 16.10.03-20230421-191025.png\" ri:version-at-save=\"1\" /></ac:image></li></ol><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>MISSION ACCOMPLISHED!  </strong><ac:emoticon ac:name=\"blue-star\" ac:emoji-shortname=\":white_check_mark:\" ac:emoji-id=\"2705\" ac:emoji-fallback=\"✅\" /><strong> </strong></p><hr /><p>Siguiente Paso: Gu&iacute;a de Acceso a Sentry &darr;</p><ac:link ac:card-appearance=\"block\"><ri:page ri:content-title=\"Qu&eacute; es Sentry y como accedo?\" ri:version-at-save=\"6\" /><ac:link-body>Gu&iacute;a de Acceso a Sentry</ac:link-body></ac:link><p> </p>","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/2580971535"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":351102963},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","schedulePublishInfo":"","metadata":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2580971535/child","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2580971535/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2580971535/history","draftVersion":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2580971535/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN"},"_links":{"editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2580971535","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2580971535/Configuraci+n+de+Reminders+en+GitHub","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2580971535","context":"/wiki","self":